bayou.http

Interface HttpEntityWrapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HttpEntity
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GzipHttpEntity, ThrottledHttpEntity

    public interface HttpEntityWrapper
extends HttpEntity
    A wrapper of HttpEntity.

    This interface implements HttpEntity methods by forwarding the calls to the origin entity. A subclass needs to implement getOriginEntity(), and selectively override some HttpEntity methods.
